{"tid":150752,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"★[IT玩完］ IT 界特首論壇 未有提出特別政綱 !","createTime":"2017-03-10T09:51:22.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-16T10:05:15.000Z","uid":19454,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"e538a2c616e6917d4b5c2a04d8d1894ede55ed5d","tid":150752,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-10T09:51:22.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://unwire.hk/2017/03/09/ceo-election-itvision-forum/hottopic/spotlight/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Funwire.hk%2F2017%2F03%2F09%2Fceo-election-itvision-forum%2Fhottopic%2Fspotlight%2F&d=TNp%2FFCzVUvAW3I%2FC9AhTYzQ9OVC7k%2FvddpU5ARN7O10%3D&h=d0ed2519\" target=\"_blank\">https://unwire.hk/2017/03/09/ceo-election-itvision-forum/hottopic/spotlight/</a><br />\n<br />\n行政長官候選人胡國興及曾俊華昨晚出席由資訊科技界選委及資訊科技界議員莫乃光舉辦的選舉論壇，而另一候選人林鄭月娥早前已拒絕出席。兩人均認為香港政府應該為創新科技產業的發展提供有利的環境及培育人才，但於論壇上並未有提出特別政綱及措施。"},{"pid":"f3351b67cd4adbe38fffc85415ba47c2335a3ccb","tid":150752,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-10T09:51:42.000Z","msg":"HK No IT"},{"pid":"333215f187fb5873a5839f47e317e4d988d67a29","tid":150752,"uid":62226,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-10T09:54:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>HK No IT</blockquote><br />\ntotally Agree"},{"pid":"829cf907315ca09c734fd5270916e4c5aa356f65","tid":150752,"uid":39866,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-10T09:57:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>HK No IT</blockquote><br />\n<br />\nIT界成班毒撚狗屎垃圾工都肯做<br />\n邊有人會肯幫呢班人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n識幾個UST grad既11k 12k都肯做<br />\n自己都唔爭氣 點幫"},{"pid":"4ebdc814df22dbb922228c476ab40d9e649e9ea4","tid":150752,"uid":49144,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-10T09:59:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>HK No IT</blockquote><br />\n<br />\nIT界成班毒撚狗屎垃圾工都肯做<br />\n邊有人會肯幫呢班人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br /